<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 00:33:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>我想相信以色列国防军不会射杀举着白旗的手无寸铁的平民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-17/ty-article/.highlight/i-want-to-believe-the-idf-wont-shoot-unarmed-civilians-holding-a-white-flag/0000018c-7896-d301-a3ac-fed78b050000</link><description>我不知道有多少人相信哈勒维所说的以色列国防军不会射杀那些投降的人。落在加沙的炸弹还导致数千名乞讨者丧生。白旗并不能阻止他们</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 21:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-17/ty-article/.highlight/i-want-to-believe-the-idf-wont-shoot-unarmed-civilians-holding-a-white-flag/0000018c-7896-d301-a3ac-fed78b050000</guid></item><item><title>六名巴勒斯坦囚犯死亡后，以色列最高法院法官将视察监狱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-supreme-court-justices-to-visit-prisons-following-deaths-of-6-palestinian-inmates/0000018c-78bb-d98c-abef-febff9290000</link><description>最近几周，关于暴力和忽视以及以色列监狱中巴勒斯坦囚犯生活条件普遍恶化的证词不断增多，导致以色列决定恢复司法探视。然而，其中一些变化是战争开始后制定的官方政策的结果，最高法院签署了该政策</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 19:11:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-supreme-court-justices-to-visit-prisons-following-deaths-of-6-palestinian-inmates/0000018c-78bb-d98c-abef-febff9290000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨致人质家属：杀害哈马斯头目辛瓦尔“根本不是重点”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/gantz-to-hostages-families-killing-hamas-chief-sinwar-not-the-point-at-all/0000018c-7874-d7be-a1cd-78fef53c0000</link><description>被哈马斯扣押的以色列人质家属在对战时内阁部长本尼·甘茨和约夫·加兰特发表讲话时，要求以色列国防军停止营救行动，并呼吁政府推动一项新协议，尽快释放剩余的俘虏。可能的</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 17:19:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/gantz-to-hostages-families-killing-hamas-chief-sinwar-not-the-point-at-all/0000018c-7874-d7be-a1cd-78fef53c0000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装加大对红海航运的攻击力度，美国警告将采取军事行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-warns-of-military-action-as-houthis-ramp-up-attacks-on-red-sea-shipping/0000018c-786b-d301-a3ac-feebbdac0000</link><description>考虑到伊朗干预的风险，拜登政府并不急于使用军事力量，而五角大楼表示，军方“将毫不犹豫地在我们认为必要和适当的情况下采取行动”</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 16:37:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-warns-of-military-action-as-houthis-ramp-up-attacks-on-red-sea-shipping/0000018c-786b-d301-a3ac-feebbdac0000</guid></item><item><title>与时间赛跑，记录 10 月 7 日以色列南部大屠杀的恐怖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-race-against-time-to-document-the-horrors-of-the-october-7-massacre-in-southern-israel/0000018c-77be-d250-a1af-ffbf61640000</link><description>一项庞大的项目正在进行中，以扫描和记录每个被烧毁的房间和扭断的窗框、每个弹孔和烧焦的椅子、每个破损的洋娃娃和废弃的仙人掌花园。就在他们于 10 月 7 日离开时，也就是哈马斯袭击以色列边境社区的那一天</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 16:24:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-race-against-time-to-document-the-horrors-of-the-october-7-massacre-in-southern-israel/0000018c-77be-d250-a1af-ffbf61640000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯社区的谋杀率自战争开始以来下降，但现在却大幅上升</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/murder-rate-in-israels-arab-communities-surges-after-plunging-since-start-of-war/0000018c-7853-d55c-a7cc-fb5793470000</link><description>哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列后，阿拉伯社区的凶杀率与战前六个月相比减少了一半，但现在已恢复到之前的水平。警方将这一上升归因于该国大部分地区恢复了相对正常的生活状态，以及现场警力的减少</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 15:53:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/murder-rate-in-israels-arab-communities-surges-after-plunging-since-start-of-war/0000018c-7853-d55c-a7cc-fb5793470000</guid></item><item><title>第三季度 GDP 下调、通胀放缓后以色列可能降息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israel-rate-cuts-possible-after-q3-gdp-revised-down-inflation-eases/0000018c-7832-d301-a3ac-fef3d4460000</link><description>2023年以色列经济增长放缓，部分原因是战争的负面影响。明年的增长很大程度上取决于战争的持续时间以及冲突是否仍然局限于加沙或蔓延到其他战线</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 15:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israel-rate-cuts-possible-after-q3-gdp-revised-down-inflation-eases/0000018c-7832-d301-a3ac-fef3d4460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙发现迄今为止最大的哈马斯隧道系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-uncovers-large-hamas-tunnel-found-so-far-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-7841-d301-a3ac-fec1da5a0000</link><description>军方称，这条隧道长四公里，宽三米，是为了车辆通过而设计的</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 15:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-uncovers-large-hamas-tunnel-found-so-far-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-7841-d301-a3ac-fec1da5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的三名士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israeli-army-names-two-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-saturday/0000018c-7816-d55c-a7cc-fb16167b0000</link><description>自以色列国防军在加沙地带开始地面行动以来，已有121名以色列士兵在哈马斯统治的加沙地带内丧生</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 14:59:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israeli-army-names-two-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-saturday/0000018c-7816-d55c-a7cc-fb16167b0000</guid></item><item><title>不仅仅是大学校园：以色列-加沙战争的紧张局势蔓延到美国公立学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-just-college-campuses-tensions-from-israel-gaza-war-spill-into-u-s-public-schools/0000018c-7733-df88-a39c-77b395160000</link><description>自10月7日以来，美国中小学反犹太事件明显增多，学生和家长对反犹太主义和反以色列对抗的加剧以及孩子们所接受的教育感到担忧</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 14:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-just-college-campuses-tensions-from-israel-gaza-war-spill-into-u-s-public-schools/0000018c-7733-df88-a39c-77b395160000</guid></item><item><title>去世前几小时，他在加沙一所学校的黑板上画下了最后的艺术作品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-drew-his-last-sketch-on-a-gaza-school-blackboard-hours-before-he-died/0000018c-691b-db38-a9fc-e9bb694b0000</link><description>尤纳坦·哈佐尔 (Yonatan Hatzor) 是一支精英部队的成员。他的创作具有人性，但他所描绘的恐怖却预示着他的死亡。 “他是我认识的最强壮的人，但他画得很精致。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 14:32:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-drew-his-last-sketch-on-a-gaza-school-blackboard-hours-before-he-died/0000018c-691b-db38-a9fc-e9bb694b0000</guid></item><item><title>这位加沙诗人在以色列空袭中丧生，突破封锁边界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/killed-in-an-israeli-airstrike-this-gaza-poet-broke-through-a-blockades-borders/0000018c-77ee-d1e1-a3ae-77eee0560000</link><description>雷法特·阿拉雷尔 (Refaat Alareer) 与几位亲密的家人一起去世，他用英语写下了加沙的生活。作为以色列的严厉批评者，他教导年轻的加沙人利用他们的写作作为巴勒斯坦抵抗的工具</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 14:04:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/killed-in-an-israeli-airstrike-this-gaza-poet-broke-through-a-blockades-borders/0000018c-77ee-d1e1-a3ae-77eee0560000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列公民和居民在战争期间在雷达之下离开加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-citizens-and-residents-left-gaza-during-the-war-under-the-radar/0000018c-77e6-de9c-aded-7fee8d700000</link><description>过去一个月，71 名妇女、男子和儿童步行、乘坐以燃气为燃料的汽车和特殊班车离开加沙地带前往以色列。他们向《国土报》讲述了自己的经历以及对那些留下来的人的担忧</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 13:41:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-citizens-and-residents-left-gaza-during-the-war-under-the-radar/0000018c-77e6-de9c-aded-7fee8d700000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙战争对以色列人来说最悲惨的时刻之一，内塔尼亚胡逃避责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/at-one-of-the-wars-most-tragic-moments-for-israelis-netanyahu-shirks-from-responsibility/0000018c-77b8-d250-a1af-ffbf782b0000</link><description>人质获释后，以色列总理欣喜若狂，但派军方发言人宣布人质死亡。内塔尼亚胡的办公室也无视人质家庭论坛的会议要求，而拜登则为美国和以色列人质家庭腾出了两个小时的时间</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 13:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/at-one-of-the-wars-most-tragic-moments-for-israelis-netanyahu-shirks-from-responsibility/0000018c-77b8-d250-a1af-ffbf782b0000</guid></item><item><title>报道哈马斯针对以色列妇女的非人性性暴力行为的伦理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/the-ethics-of-covering-hamas-dehumanizing-sexual-violence-against-israeli-women/0000018c-5e45-d798-adac-feef6cb80000</link><description>以色列应该小心，不要让其对打击针对妇女的性暴力的国际组织可耻的无动于衷的愤怒，不要演变成对哈马斯战争罪行受害者的人性和隐私的难以承受的打击。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 12:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/the-ethics-of-covering-hamas-dehumanizing-sexual-violence-against-israeli-women/0000018c-5e45-d798-adac-feef6cb80000</guid></item><item><title>释放我儿子的巴勒斯坦杀手，以释放哈马斯扣押的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/free-my-sons-palestinian-killer-to-free-the-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018c-76ce-db38-a9fc-ffee21580000</link><description>只要婴儿、父亲、母亲和兄弟仍被困在加沙，整个以色列都是哈马斯的人质，人质家庭的处境最为严重。这就是为什么我呼吁释放杀害我心爱儿子的狙击手，如果这能带回他们的亲人之一</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 11:43:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/free-my-sons-palestinian-killer-to-free-the-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018c-76ce-db38-a9fc-ffee21580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列枪支许可机构负责人表示，本-格维尔的政策导致“失控”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/head-of-israels-gun-licensing-authority-ben-gvirs-policy-leading-to-loss-of-control/0000018c-767f-db38-a9fc-fffffa160000</link><description>负责批准枪支许可证的以色列官员敦促极右翼部长改变其政策，因为有消息称本-格维尔的同伙已被任命在未经必要授权的情况下处理请求</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 11:14:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/head-of-israels-gun-licensing-authority-ben-gvirs-policy-leading-to-loss-of-control/0000018c-767f-db38-a9fc-fffffa160000</guid></item><item><title>五名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸丧生，四人死于以色列军队无人机袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-four-from-israeli-army-drone-strike/0000018c-7731-dabb-afae-77b355360000</link><description>这次袭击是在巴勒斯坦城市图尔卡尔姆连夜进行的，是以色列国防军自战争开始以来在该地区第二次“制止恐怖”行动之际进行的</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 11:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-four-from-israeli-army-drone-strike/0000018c-7731-dabb-afae-77b355360000</guid></item><item><title>法国外交部称工人在以色列对加沙拉法的袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/french-foreign-ministry-says-worker-killed-by-an-israeli-strike-in-gazas-rafah/0000018c-7724-dbd5-a39c-ff772e860000</link><description>法国外交部表示，我们要求以色列当局尽快全面了解这次爆炸事件的情况。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 09:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/french-foreign-ministry-says-worker-killed-by-an-israeli-strike-in-gazas-rafah/0000018c-7724-dbd5-a39c-ff772e860000</guid></item><item><title>半岛电视台将以色列袭击导致加沙摄影师死亡案件移交国际刑事法院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/al-jazeera-to-refer-death-of-cameraman-in-gaza-from-israeli-strike-to-icc/0000018c-76e1-dbd5-a39c-fff376d80000</link><description>据半岛电视台报道，摄影师萨米尔·阿布·达卡 (Samer Abu Daqqa) 在报道早些时候对加沙学校的爆炸事件时在以色列无人机袭击中身亡。以色列国防军表示“从未”故意针对记者</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 09:24:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/al-jazeera-to-refer-death-of-cameraman-in-gaza-from-israeli-strike-to-icc/0000018c-76e1-dbd5-a39c-fff376d80000</guid></item></channel></rss>